Do. 5 1/2 % 3rd Cm. Pf. 1.925p
Lucas Inds. 6 1/2 % Cm. 1st Pf. 2.275p
Merchant Retail 0.2p
Metropolitan Water Board 3% 1934/2003 Pounds 1.50
Do. Mexico 16 1/2 % Ln. 2008 Pounds 8.25
National Home Loans Sec. FRN 1995 Dollars 1.40
Oldham Metropolitan Borough Council 11.25% Rd. 2010 Pounds 5.625
Parkland 4.2% Cm. Pf. 2.1p
P &amp; O 3 1/2 % Db. Pounds 1.75
